author: wn.com
title: Washington's Allies in Syria Are 'Endangered Species Soon to Go Extinct'
text: As Russia continues its military engagement in Syria assisting Bashar al-Assad in his fight against the Islamic State, Washington's allies in the Middle East will likely increasingly support other radical groups trying to remove Assad from power, the National Interest observed. ...
